deferlay - defers gentoo portage overlay
========================================

info
----
This repository contains ebuild script. Portage package manager uses ebuild
scripts to download, configure, build and install packages from sources.

goal
----
The main goal is to maintain packages that i personally use,
but i can also create ebuilds on request.

contents
--------
git versions of packages
latest versions waiting for addition to official portage tree
packages that cant be found from official portage tree

install
-------
layman:
emerge -av layman
layman -a deferlay
emerge -av scron

manual:
git clone https://github.com/defer-/deferlay
echo 'PORTDIR_OVERLAY="/home/username/deferlay"' >> /etc/portage/make.conf
emerge -av scron
